# Approval Workflow

## Roles
- Owner: can edit canon, approve package tiers, and authorize exports
- Editor: can refine generated docs and request regeneration
- Producer: can approve finance and production assumptions
- Legal reviewer: can approve public and rights-sensitive language
- Publicist: can approve press and website content

## Lock Rules
- `locked` canon fields should not be changed without explicit owner review
- `approved` public fields may flow to website outputs
- `draft` fields may appear in internal docs but should not be treated as final

## Regeneration Rules
- Whole package: use when canon changes broadly
- Department regeneration: use when only one area needs refresh
- Single file regeneration: use when preserving the rest of the package state
